        <abstract>
            <p>Will support the petition for a pension for Wallace.</p> 
<p>CD’s paragraph [about Wyville Thomson, see <hi rend="doubleUnderline">12796</hi>] was so good that if he had written it he would have sent it to the printer, but [for CD] it is best to refrain.</p> 
